Uses of QueueDiscipline in jsl.modeling.elements.queue
 

Subclasses of QueueDiscipline in jsl.modeling.elements.queue
 class FIFODiscipline
          The FIFODiscipline provides a mechanism to the Queue object for ordering the elements according to the first in, first out rule.
 class LIFODiscipline
          The LIFODiscipline provides a mechanism to the Queue object for ordering the elements according to the first in, first out rule.
 class RandomDiscipline
          The RandomDiscipline provides a mechanism to the Queue object to provide a random selection of objects from the queue rule.
 class RankedQDiscipline
          The RankedQDiscipline provides a mechanism to the Queue object for ordering the elements according to a priority rule.
